channel.description:
Hello!
After trying to fix library errors for more than an hour, I finally lost that error, but I started getting a new one:
``` Severity Code Description Project File Line Suppression State Error LNK2001 unresolved external symbol "public: void __cdecl KeyAuth::api::check(void)" (?check@api@KeyAuth@@QEAAXXZ) example C:\Users\user\Desktop\KeyAuth-CPP-Example-main\main.obj 1 ``` Any Ideas on how to fix it? VS 2022, the only thing I updated was library_x64 as I couldnt find libcurl 64 version for 2022.... I already read another thread regarding this error but it did not answer my question. Thank you in advance!
